-- Citigroup Says Euro-Area Chief Economist Michels Has Left
-- B y   S t e f a n   R i e c h e r
-- 2013-05-07T12:03:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-05-07/citigroup-says-euro-area-chief-economist-michels-has-left.html
Juergen Michels, chief euro-area
economist and managing director at  Citigroup Inc. (C)  in London, has
left the company.  “I can confirm that he has left Citigroup to pursue new
opportunities,” Frankfurt-based spokeswoman Anette Baum said by
telephone. She said she doesn’t know his future plans.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stefan Riecher in Frankfurt at 
